{
  "stem": "13096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the people-- [INTERPOSING VOICES] --who were put into the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were putted-- assigned to the left and to the right, our group, that were to survive, we went to the right by foot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taken for few minutes to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This barrack, you know, we stayed there until nighttime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at the same times, they send us, you know, to the right, to the left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The people to the right were divided in two groups-- male and female.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we arrived to this barrack after a few-- like you say, 1/2 an hour march, we were telled to rest there for a little while.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The little while stretch out till nighttime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nighttime came, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought us-- the men, as well, of our group-- for five minutes to the other side of the room to show us, I suppose, who were the survivor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we didn't know at the time what it meant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very dark room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put the men from one side and the women to the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That is, the women and men that they were waiting to survive-- that they were going to go to the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They switched it on the light, for five minutes, and we can see each other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After five minutes, the lights were back again dark, and the men were taken away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we women were told to go-- but still, you know, the whole day without food-- to go to another room.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first thing we do-- we did during that night-- that time-- it was already 2 o'clock at night-- they took us to a place where they were prisoners-- barbers, or whatever you call it-- with shavers.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
